d in auditing Agile projects. This makes it an ideal book for any auditor encountering the Agile methodology, and any Agile teams preparing for a management audit. This book will enable you to: understand the principles of Agile appreciate how it might be effectively audited improve communication between the auditor and the Agile team. Read this book to understand how to get the most out of Agile audits, whatever your role.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aAgile software development. 0aAuditing. 0aComputer softwarexDevelopment. 7aCOMPUTERS / Desktop Applications / Project Management Software.2bisacsh  aAgile.  aIT Audit.  aProject management.  aagile methodologies.  aagile team.  aaudit.  aauditing.  agovernance.  ainternal audit.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSciendo All Ebooks Trial Collection 2024z97831115024960 cEPUBz978184928589640uhttps://sciendo.com/book/9781849285889  a978-3-11-150249-6  Sciendo All Ebooks Trial Collection 2024b2024  aGBV-deGruyter-alles